### 设置index中的文档属性采用ik分词   目前所学的，只有text支持分词
POST http://localhost:9200/questions/_mapping
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": {
    "title": {
      "type": "text",
      "analyzer": "ik_max_word",
      "search_analyzer": "ik_max_word"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "analyzer": "ik_max_word",
      "search_analyzer": "ik_max_word"
    }
  }
}
