### 搜素 ES  match即模糊查询
POST http://localhost:9200/questions/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": { "match": {"title": "类型" } }
}
### 多字段搜索
POST http://localhost:9200/questions/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": {
    "bool": {
      "should": [
        { "match": { "title":  "java类型" }},
        { "match": { "content": "java类型"}}
      ]
    }
  }
}


### 条件搜索，查询用户12 或者 公开的 同时 标题或者内容中包含Java的问题
POST http://localhost:9200/wenwenti/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": {
    "bool": {
      "must": [{
        "bool": {
          "should": [{"match": {"title": "java"}}, {"match": {"content": "java"}}]
        }
      }, {
        "bool": {
          "should": [{"term": {"publicStatus": 1}}, {"term": {"userId": 11}}]
        }
      }]
    }
  }
}